Class DslTestBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • euporia.tecnling.retoricaweb.dsl.dsltest.DslTestBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DslTestListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DslTestImplListener

    public class DslTestBaseListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements DslTestListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of DslTestListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
